edu.gmu.ttaconline.atcguide

Class PersistenceBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.gmu.ttaconline.atcguide.PersistenceBean

  • public class PersistenceBean
extends java.lang.Object
    ORM for ATGuide application Java bean to persist data to the SQLite DB. Storing details of current intent and retrieving all previous values utilizing the helper and contract classes This class is the part of the ATGUIDE application built for KIHD, CEHD, GMU. Spring 2017
    Author:
    Animesh Jain | Java programmer -CEHD GMU |MS CS class of 2018
